{"title":"Manim1 Installation","uid":"45e3d46203ca5cc5718cda218b7c4f03","slug":"manim/C1 installation","date":"2021-08-26T03:46:33.000Z","updated":"2021-08-26T07:58:07.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/manim/C1 installation.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"manim安装-MacOS\"><a href=\"#manim安装-MacOS\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"manim安装(MacOS)\"></a>manim安装(MacOS)</h1><h2 id=\"相关依赖项的安装\"><a href=\"#相关依赖项的安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"相关依赖项的安装\"></a>相关依赖项的安装</h2><p><a href=\"https://docs.manim.community/en/stable/installation/mac.html\">https://docs.manim.community/en/stable/installation/mac.html</a></p>\n<p>To install cairo:</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> cairo<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>To install ffmpeg:</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> ffmpeg<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>To install LaTeX:</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> --cask mactex<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"安装manim\"><a href=\"#安装manim\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装manim\"></a>安装manim</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">pip3 <span class=\"token function\">install</span> manim<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"快速入门\"><a href=\"#快速入门\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"快速入门\"></a>快速入门</h2><h3 id=\"first-Scene代码说明\"><a href=\"#first-Scene代码说明\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"first Scene代码说明\"></a>first Scene代码说明</h3><p>To produce your first scene, create a new file in your project folder called <code>scene.py</code>,</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">project&#x2F;\n└─scene.py<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><code>scene.py</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> manim <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">#从mainm库中导入所有内容</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">SquareToCircle</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Scene<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">construct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        circle <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Circle<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># create a circle</span>\n        circle<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>set_fill<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>PINK<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> opacity<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># set the color and transparency</span>\n        self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>play<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Create<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>circle<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># show the circle on screen</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>代码说明</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">SquareToCircle</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Scene<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">construct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>创建对象、将其显示在屏幕上并为其设置动画</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">circle <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Circle<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># create a circle</span>\n        circle<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>set_fill<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>PINK<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> opacity<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># set the color and transparency</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>创建一个圆圈并设置其颜色和不透明度</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>play<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Create<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>circle<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># show the circle on screen</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>使用动画在屏幕上显示圆</p>\n<h3 id=\"测试\"><a href=\"#测试\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"测试\"></a>测试</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">manim -pql scene.py SquareToCircle\n<span class=\"token comment\">#-p 渲染后播放场景</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">#-ql 告诉manim以低质量渲染场景</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># -qh 则为高质量</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gtu8x297ifj62580deq5h02.jpg\" alt=\"截屏2021-08-09 下午7.14.17\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">project&#x2F;\n├─scene.py\n└─media\n  ├─videos\n  |  └─scene\n  |     └─480p15\n  |        ├─SquareToCircle.mp4\n  |        └─partial_movie_files\n  ├─text\n  └─Tex<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">manim render --help\n<span class=\"token comment\">#官方帮助文档</span>\nmanim scene.py SquareToCircle -i \n<span class=\"token comment\">#导出为GIF</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gtu8x65a6jg61hc0u0q5802.gif\" alt=\"SquareToCircle_ManimCE_v0.9.0\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"进一步调整\"><a href=\"#进一步调整\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"进一步调整\"></a>进一步调整</h2><h3 id=\"代码说明\"><a href=\"#代码说明\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码说明\"></a>代码说明</h3><p><code>scene2.py</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> manim <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">SquareToCircle</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Scene<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">construct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        circle <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Circle<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># create a circle</span>\n        circle<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>set_fill<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>PINK<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> opacity<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0.5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># set color and transparency</span>\n\n        square <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Square<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># create a square</span>\n        square<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>rotate<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>PI <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># rotate a certain amount</span>\n\n        self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>play<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Create<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>square<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># animate the creation of the square</span>\n        self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>play<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Transform<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>square<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> circle<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># interpolate the square into the circle</span>\n        self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>play<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>FadeOut<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>square<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># fade out animation</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"测试-1\"><a href=\"#测试-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"测试\"></a>测试</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">manim -pql scene2.py SquareToCircle<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gtu8xadq9sj61pk0kw0ws02.jpg\" alt=\"截屏2021-08-09 下午7.27.34\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">manim scene2.py SquareToCircle -i <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/008i3skNly1gtu8xcp079g61hc0u0nj602.gif\" alt=\"SquareToCircle_ManimCE_v0.9.0\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"一些line-flags\"><a href=\"#一些line-flags\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一些line flags\"></a>一些line flags</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">manim -pql scene.py SquareToCircle -i\n<span class=\"token comment\">#低质量gif导出</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.manim.community/en/stable/tutorials/configuration.html\">https://docs.manim.community/en/stable/tutorials/configuration.html</a></p>\n","text":"manim安装(MacOS)相关依赖项的安装https://docs.manim.community/en/stable/installation/mac.html To install cairo: brew install cairo To install ffmpeg: b...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Manim","slug":"Manim","count":3,"path":"api/categories/Manim.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Manim","slug":"Manim","count":3,"path":"api/tags/Manim.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#manim%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-MacOS\"><span class=\"toc-text\">manim安装(MacOS)</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E9%A1%B9%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">相关依赖项的安装</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85manim\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装manim</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">快速入门</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#first-Scene%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E\"><span class=\"toc-text\">first Scene代码说明</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">测试</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BF%9B%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">进一步调整</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%AF